text: Domadugu is a census town in Sangareddy district of the Indian state of Telangana. == Geography == It is located at . ==Accessibility== Domadugu is 37 km from Hyderabad and can be reached by TSRTC buses. ==Neighborhoods== Gummadidala, Annaram, Bonthapally , Dundigal == References == Category:Cities and towns in Sangareddy district Category:Cities and towns in Telangana
